<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>driving test • test drive</xh5><p> <i>driving test—</i>an examination of a person’s ability to drive a car: What is wanted is a more radical reform in the <u>driving test</u> calculated to lift the standard of roadcraft.</p><p> <i>test drive—</i>a drive in a car one thinks of buying, etc. to judge its qualities: Before signing a satisfaction note inspect the vehicle carefully and, if possible, take it for a <u>test drive</u>.</p> </entry>
